**Gregory P. Finley II** (born December 22, 1984) in Portland, Maine, is an
[American](/wiki/United_States "United States") actor, best known for his role
as [Jack Pappas](/wiki/Jack_Pappas "Jack Pappas") in the teenage drama series
_[The Secret Life of the American
Teenager](/wiki/The_Secret_Life_of_the_American_Teenager "The Secret Life of
the American Teenager")_ as well as Drake in the series _[Star
Crossed](/wiki/Star-Crossed_\(TV_series\) "Star-Crossed \(TV series\)"),
[iZombie](/wiki/IZombie_\(TV_series\) "IZombie \(TV series\)")_ and
[Girder](/wiki/List_of_Flash_enemies "List of Flash enemies") in [_The
Flash_](/wiki/The_Flash_\(2014_TV_series\) "The Flash \(2014 TV series\)").

Finley is best known for his role as Jack Pappas, on _The Secret Life Of The
American Teenager_.[1] In February 2010, Finley was cast in the Dark Sky Films
thriller _[Hypothermia](/wiki/Hypothermia\(film\) "Hypothermia\(film\)")_ ,
directed by [James Felix McKenney](/wiki/James_Felix_McKenney "James Felix
McKenney").[2]
